data.description: What a find! A sprawling ranch-style home w/ 6+ bedrooms, 4 baths, an att. two car garage, large lot, close to schools! Main level features hardwood floors throughout the main living room & bedrooms, functional kitchen leading to a large family room/dining area, primary bedroom suite w/ bath & laundry. 5 bedrooms and 2 of the baths are on the main level. The basement offers a game room w/ projector, the 6th bedroom (w/ egress), 2 bathrooms, plentiful storage, second laundry, and several other flex rooms - perfect for crafts, toys, home office/business, storage, studio, etc. Don't forget the large yard & patio, complete w/ an awning. This home is set up well with 2 furnaces, 2 water heaters, and 2 central air units.There's an additional 12x24 shed for storage/hobbies. Endless possibilities.
